www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/07\/24\/urwah-no-iman-cannot-trust\/","url_meta":{"origin":19150,"position":0},"title":"Urwah on Trust: No faith for one who cannot be trusted","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Hisham ibn 'Urwah reported: 'Urwah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cBe not deceived by the prayer of a man, nor by his fasting. Whoever wills can fast and whoever wills can pray, yet there is no religion for one who cannot be trusted.\u201d Source: al-\u012ama\u0304n li Ibn Abi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25325,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/25\/bismillah-before-wudu\/","url_meta":{"origin":19150,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Recommendation to mention Allah before ablution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 25, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no prayer for one without ablution, and there is no ablution for one without mentioning the name of Allah before it.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 101 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani Al-Marghinani said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39838,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/21\/shahadah-necessitates-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":19150,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Shahadah: Testimony of faith necessitates Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 21, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Suhayl ibn Bayda\u2019 reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, whoever testifies there is no God but Allah, then Allah will forbid him from entering Hellfire and require him to enter Paradise.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 199 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21031,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/10\/13\/fatwa-hikmah-ibn-abbas\/","url_meta":{"origin":19150,"position":3},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Fatwa: Wisdom in issuing legal verdicts","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 13, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d ibn 'Ubaydah reported: A man came to Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, and he said, \u201cIs there repentance for one who kills a believer?\u201d Ibn Abbas said, \u201cNo, there is nothing but Hellfire.\u201d After the man left, those sitting nearby said to him, \u201cWhat is this?\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24287,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/01\/22\/ali-sabr-iman-head-body\/","url_meta":{"origin":19150,"position":4},"title":"Ali on Sabr: Patience to faith like a head to a body","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"Jan